	<td class="alt2" valign="top">
	
	<!-- message -->
	<p>I got my Acrylia Shard last night. We camped the Arcanist who drops a 14/22 1hs and 36/40 2hs (which looks like RZTW sword, let the safehouse whining commence!)... To get there you head to the big room with the buildings, then head up the steps past the undead (gotta kill them, they see invis) Then go to the right where the ring of the High priest used to be. Click on the little statue thingy and you're inside Inner Acrylia. From the room where you enter. go north and down some stairs, and into a room with a table with lots of grimlings, and a "jail" type room off to the west end. We camped here for about 3 hours... We didn't see anything for 2 hours, then got 3 shards in 15 minutes time, off of the mobs called "A Sanctum Bloodguard"<br />
<br />
Random stuff sees invis there, hits for 160 or so, and has around 10-12k hit points... I wasn't able to single mobs at 64, and there really isn't much room. It's probably soloabe but CRing if you get unlucky would be a bitch and a half. My strategy was to trick some people by bringing them to "Check out inner acrylia" and secretly get my shard <img src="images/smilies/biggrin.gif" border="0" alt="" title="big grin" smilieid="4" /></p>
	
	
	
