	<td class="alt1" valign="top">
	
	<!-- message -->
	<p>I just solo'ed the new acrylia caverns shard.  Its probably easier to do now then it was before.  Just harder to get to the area then it was before. I set up shop where the gate is into the building area.  Then I started pulling all that stood in the way of the statue that warps you into inner acrylia.  Took about 40 mins for me and dogdog to get past all of those mobs.  You could probably invis after you kill the undead or even use IVU potions to pass the undead and then use regular invis to get to the statue.  But I wanted to take my time and ease my way in.  Once in inner acrylia just kill, kill, and kill.  I just root parked and let dogdog tank em.  I got mostly 75% of the mobs single, but occasionally I would get an add but it wasnt anything me and spirit call 3 couldnt handle.  My shard dropped off a santum bloodguard.  Hope this helps any of you other shaman that need to get the shard.  <img src="images/smilies/smile.gif" border="0" alt="" title="smile" smilieid="1" /><br />
<br />
Avoozl Ravensfeather<br />
Prophet of Vazaelle</p>
	
	
	
	
	
