	<!-- message -->
	<p>Just wanted to add the FG is really easy to solo, there is 2 warriors on a hill before you turn to where the warlord spawns. At 65 it was a very peaceful camp that i didnt have to even pay attention to. You can single pull from the walls and  once they down there is plenty of downtime for you to go afk and do somehting in RL. Dreaded this camp hardcore, but it was probably one of the easiest for a shaman. Max hit was 171 i think, nothing puppy couldnt handle with Q once in a while. got another 15% AAin a casual camp in about 1 maybe 1.2 hours. Next weeks patch would allow you to kill more of them for more XP so would probably be even better as the soldiers were only LB to me at 65</p>
	
	
	
	
	
