<tr>
	<td class="alt1" width="175" align="center" valign="top" nowrap="nowrap"><b>bakkal</b>
<span class="smallfont">
	<br />
	Disciple<br />
		
	
	<br />
	Joined: Jan 2002<br />
	Location: Atlanta, GA
</span></td>
	
	<td class="alt1" valign="top">
	
	<!-- message -->
	<p>I don't see why you couldn't solo/duo/trio SSRA mines. I've done it with 4 with shaman as the CC (me)  We didn't really need the 4, I was 2boxing cleric/shaman and other was on Wiz/Paladin.<br />
<br />
You would have to have an IVU potion to get to the bottom where they drop the most, pull with AE slow or root most likely.  As soon as you get them all rooted away you could work on one.  It wouldn't be very enjoyable, but I don't see why it couldn't be done.  I'd much prefer the most people possible to kill off the mines, but it would be a doable challenge.  <br />
<br />
With AE slow, fast cast root/slow, and not much being resisted, it does'nt seem like it'd be all that difficult.  Be ready for a rez though, I'd imagine it'd be reasonably high risk if everything didn't go real well.</p>
	
	
	
	
	
		<div class="smallfont"><a href="report.php?s=d7ccf0baa7a88668bb17ca76c6b64db8&amp;postid=155505">Report Post</a> | IP: <a href="postings.php?s=d7ccf0baa7a88668bb17ca76c6b64db8&amp;do=getip&postid=155505">Logged</a></div>
	
